This paper discusses a method for data annotation in natural language processing, specifically sentiment intensity annotation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques and data analysis, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the reliability of the annotation method, which could be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
